WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
My name is Rikala Guru Krishna Kumar. I am an advocate on the Supreme Court of India.

00:06.000 --> 00:12.000
We have our own lawyers office for more than 12 to 15 years now.

00:12.000 --> 00:19.000
I have been making investments in the stock market and through mutual funds with integrated enterprises.

00:19.000 --> 00:25.000
They were first introduced to me by our chartered accountant who recommended that

00:25.000 --> 00:34.000
they are very transparent stock brokers and will ensure that there are no problems in the investment procedures.

00:34.000 --> 00:37.000
They will not mislead you with the types of investments.

00:37.000 --> 00:45.000
Accordingly, we had started investments. Our one stop contact point and the earlier stages was Shama in the Karol Boga office

00:45.000 --> 00:52.000
who was extremely helpful and who would continuously follow up on the status of our investments.

00:52.000 --> 00:57.000
I recommend what we have to sell, recommend those which are not worthwhile to hold on to

00:57.000 --> 01:03.000
and ensure that we sold them at the correct time and also advises on purchases.

01:03.000 --> 01:08.000
We had many relationship managers from various banks where we held accounts,

01:08.000 --> 01:14.000
but guidance given by integrated enterprises has always been very useful and grounded

01:14.000 --> 01:18.000
without any misleading information for any vested interests.

01:19.000 --> 01:24.000
Recently we have been touched with Mr. Ganesh also who has also been advising us

01:24.000 --> 01:29.000
in an overall manner about the investments for both me and my husband.

01:29.000 --> 01:33.000
I think their investment profile has been good and we have made decent profits

01:33.000 --> 01:35.000
with the investments made through them.

01:35.000 --> 01:38.000
Best of luck to them on their completion of 50 years.

